# TweakCN Supabase Theme Styling Guide

## **MANDATORY STYLING REQUIREMENTS**

All UI components and changes MUST follow this TweakCN Supabase theme styling guide to maintain design consistency.

## **Color System**

### **Primary Colors**
- **Primary**: `oklch(0.8348 0.1302 160.9080)` - Teal/Green accent
- **Primary Foreground**: `oklch(0.2626 0.0147 166.4589)` - Dark text on primary
- **Background**: `oklch(0.9911 0 0)` (light) / `oklch(0.1822 0 0)` (dark)
- **Foreground**: `oklch(0.2046 0 0)` (light) / `oklch(0.9288 0.0126 255.5078)` (dark)

### **Semantic Colors**
- **Card**: `oklch(0.9911 0 0)` (light) / `oklch(0.2046 0 0)` (dark)
- **Muted**: `oklch(0.9461 0 0)` (light) / `oklch(0.2393 0 0)` (dark)
- **Accent**: `oklch(0.9461 0 0)` (light) / `oklch(0.3132 0 0)` (dark)
- **Border**: `oklch(0.9037 0 0)` (light) / `oklch(0.2809 0 0)` (dark)

### **Sidebar Colors**
- **Sidebar**: `oklch(0.9911 0 0)` (light) / `oklch(0.1822 0 0)` (dark)
- **Sidebar Primary**: `oklch(0.8348 0.1302 160.9080)` - Teal accent
- **Sidebar Accent**: `oklch(0.9461 0 0)` (light) / `oklch(0.3132 0 0)` (dark)

